This is a tool to modify you template threshold file to catch error done by NaN number
When we make rate ther is often a division that can be a NaN number. We choose apply an
error but to make it green with this script, but you can also change the color (default to clear)

Instrtuction
1. Place all your templates (or part of it), in the template folder located in this script folder
2. Execute the script:do_add_NaN_thresholds (this will generate a script also in this script folder 
3. Execute the script generated: do_modify (this will modify the templates that you place in this script folder)
4. The template are modified, you will have now to move them back your in the right folder
